high_descs: Walk to the wall, then turn left and walk over to the round wooden table.
Pick up the sponge off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn right again and walk up to the wooden table.
Put the sponge on the closest grey plate that is on the table.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it off of the table.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left again and walk to the counter.
Open the right lower cabinet door and put the plate with the sponge on it inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a sponge on it in a cabinet.

high_descs: turn around, walk to face the wooden round table
pick up the green sponge from the table top
walk slightly left to still face the table
place the sponge on the plate on the right on the table
pick up the plate from the table top
turn to walk to face the microwave
open the cabinet below microwave, put sponge inside cabinet, close the door
anns.task_desc: put a sponge and plate in a kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Walk in the direction of the door, hang a left to the round table in the corner to the left of the door.
Pick up the green sponge sitting to the right of the coffee maker.
Walk to the left side of the table.
Place the sponge on the plate directly in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it.
Turn around and walk to the cupboard below the counter that the microwave is sitting on.
Open the cupboard door on the right, place the plate with the sponge on it in the cupboard, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge on a plate, place the plate in the cupboard under the microwave
